# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Generated data and model artifacts
#
# Synthetic audio, corpora, and checkpoints are distributed separately (see
# docs/DATA.md), not committed. Result JSONs under results/ ARE committed --
# they are the evidence behind the paper's tables and are small.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
data/
generated_audio/
generated_audio*/
*.bak/
checkpoints/
wandb/
*.pth
*.pt
*.bin
*.safetensors
*.ckpt
*.wav
*.mp3
*.flac
*.parquet

