# Archives
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.7z
*.zip
*.tar
*.tar.gz

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Run logs
#
# Training transcripts are not reproducibility evidence and contain absolute
# local paths. The JSON summaries in results/ carry the numbers.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.log
logs/

